race.comment: CHARTIN (5) is knocking on the door after three straight placings, the latest a strong second at Strathalbyn. Unbeaten over this trip, gets in light with the 3kg claim, and draws perfectly. Ready to strike. SPACE EQUITY (1) was dominant last start at Penola over this journey. Carries more weight but can go back-to-back. READY BY DESIGN (4) made late ground for second first-up at Avoca and strips fitter. Right race, winning chance. BADONKIDONK (2) was unsuited fresh but now steps up to his preferred trip and gets Crowther. Sharp improvement expected. Keep safe. FOUR OUTLAWS (3) couldn't repeat his win last time but finds a suitable race and can bounce back.
